PartyGirl: {
	NPC: {
		Puro: I love to party with Puro! He is a real party animal!
		Prototype: "{NamePrototype} is a real party machine. He can play music and act as a disco ball at the same time."
		Scientist: None
	}

	Transfur: {
		BlackGoop: Wow, the chocolate cake is moving! Now that is a cool party trick!
		WhiteGoop: Wow, the cake is moving! Now that is a cool party trick!
