		WhiteCub: Hello! Are you here for the pet party?
		SquidDog: Let's dance! Give me your hand! Or both hands. Uh, or... four hands?
	}
}

Pirate: {
	NPC: {
		Puro: Ahoy, me takes that blackbeard wolf under me wing, landlubber. Me love raisin' sea pups!
		Prototype: None
		Scientist: Arrr, that scientist be looking as pale as a ghost. Me thinks he be cursed.
	}

	Transfur: {
		BlackGoop: Stand still ye blob 'o tar. I need ye to fix the hole in me ship!
		WhiteGoop: Stand still ye blob 'o tar. I need ye to fix the hole in me ship!
		BlackCub: Yar, ye be the most adorable sea pup me has ever seen!
		WhiteCub: Yar, ye be the most adorable sea pup me has ever seen!
		SquidDog: Arr, what sea monster might ye be? A canine kraken?
	}
}

SantaClaus: {
	NPC: {
		Puro: I can give almost anything as a gift, and then there is that one person who has put nothing but oranges on their wish list.
		Prototype: My elves should make a toy version of {NamePrototype}. I'm sure the kids will love it.
		Scientist: I will add Doctor K to the naughty list, because he does not believe in me.
	}

	Transfur: {
		BlackGoop: None
		WhiteGoop: None
		BlackCub: Perhaps I should put you in a gift box and give you to someone who wants a puppy for Christmas.
		WhiteCub: Perhaps I should put you in a gift box and give you to someone who wants a puppy for Christmas.
		SquidDog: I don't know who you are, but you are definitely on the naughty list!
	}
}

