TaxCollector: {
	NPC: {
		Puro: If that black jelly wolf doesn't pay rent soon, I will charge him animal tax too!
		Prototype: Thanks to that oversized microwave called {NamePrototype} the energy bill has more than doubled!
		Scientist: Doctor K said he paid the rent, but the figures don't add up. I bet he has a PhD in tax evasion!
	}

	Transfur: {
		BlackGoop: Bah! Who forgot to wipe their shoes? Now there is mud everywhere!
		WhiteGoop: Bah! Who forgot to wipe their shoes? Now there is mud everywhere!
		BlackCub: Go away mutt! {NamePlayer} only has a license for one dog!
		WhiteCub: Go away mutt! {NamePlayer} only has a license for one dog!
		BlackCubNoLicense: Go away mutt! And don't come back until {NamePlayer} has bought a dog license!
		WhiteCubNoLicense: Go away mutt! And don't come back until {NamePlayer} has bought a dog license!
		SquidDog: Shoo! Go bother someone else you stupid sea monster!
	}
}

